# Deployment Owner

The deployment owner username defaults to the **company display name** from admin → Profile (override per install with `ADMIN_USERNAME`, comma-separated for multiple names).

Owner-only UI today:
- **Plugins** page (account menu → Plugins)
- `GET` / `PUT` `/api/admin/features`

Match is case-insensitive against the signed-in Clerk user's id (`AGENT_ALERT_USER_ID`), or `username`, `firstName`, `lastName`, full name, or primary email (full or local part).

Other signed-in users can use the rest of admin; they do not see Plugins or manage feature toggles.
